title: (Fri Full Show) Lainey Wilson's In-Studio Talking About Her New Album Out Today, Being On Yellowstone and More! + Is What Happened To Amy's Son Okay? + Easy Trivia!
itunes:title: (Fri Full Show) Lainey Wilson's In-Studio Talking About Her New Album Out Today, Being On Yellowstone and More! + Is What Happened To Amy's Son Okay? + Easy Trivia!
description:
Lainey Wilson is in-studio with us today talking about her new album "Bell Bottom Country" that is out today! She also shares details about her new character she's playing on the new season of Yellowstone coming out soon, and more! Plus, Amy shares a story of something that happened to her son recently and she's not sure what to do about it... Then, we play 'Easy Trivia!' The show answers easy questions, find out who loses this time!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
